title: Apartment Glow Up & Toxic Femininity
description:
Tasia and Camo are back together again, recording outside in the beautiful spring air!! Tasia updates everyone on her big move and stresses the importance of finding the right furniture for your home and Camo fills us in on the Johnny Depp drama. The two of them discuss their thoughts on the matter and dive into what toxic femininity can look like. You won't want to miss this juicy episode!
Watch "Unfazed and Unbothered" on YouTube
If you like the show, telling a friend about it would be helpful! You can text, email, Tweet, or send this link to a friend: https://bit.ly/UnfazedandUnbotheredPodcast
